---
title: Teriyaki Tofu Bulgur Bowl with smashed cucumber and pickled radish
description: Smashed cucumber and pickled radish add a bit of bite—in more ways than one—to this abundant bulgur bowl. Protein-packed tofu is coated in sticky and sweet teriyaki sauce for a nourishing element white toasted sesame seeds add a wonderful nuttiness to this fantastic veggie dish.
